snippet: Russell Henley ran off eight birdies on a gorgeous day with little wind for an eight-under-par 65, in the opening round of the Hyundai Tournament of Champions in Kapalua, Hawaii.
abstract: Russell Henley takes first-round lead at Hyundai Tournament of Champions golf event in Hawaii; other golf news noted.
